word_mean_info__list.difference: 可替换disagree，但语气较温和，是disagree的委婉说法。
指彼此间意见或看法不同，任何言行上的不合。
语气强烈，侧重对某一具体计划、行为或作法等表示反对。常跟前置词to连用。

word_group.brief_definition: 同意保留不同意见；同意各执己见；保留不同意见

bilingual.source: I'm afraid that I have to disagree.

bilingual.target: 我们在这个问题上不同意。

bilingual.source: If you disagree, please let me know.
bilingual.target: 如果你不同意，请告诉我。

bilingual.source: I disagree with your opinion on this matter.
bilingual.target: 我不同意你在这件事上的看法。

bilingual.source: He tends to dis people who disagree with him.
bilingual.target: 他倾向于不尊重那些不同意他的人。

bilingual.source: He tends to contemn those who disagree with him.
bilingual.target: 他倾向于轻视那些不同意他的人。

yingyinNormal.en: I disagree. It wasn't just me. It was all of us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不同意，不只是我，是我们所有人。

yingyinNormal.en: You can quote them, disagree with them, glorify or vilify them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以给他们加上引号，不同意他们的观点，赞美或诽谤他们。

yingyinNormal.en: I think we should merge. I disagree. They're offering us equal spots on management committees.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得我们应该合并。我不同意。他们给予我们一半的管理委员会席位。

yingyinNormal.en: I know someone who would disagree. Who? My physics bowl trophy. Leonard is so smart. Sheldon who?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道有人不同意。谁？我的物理碗奖杯，莱纳德真聪明，谢尔顿是谁？

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, you're not helping. Disagree. Go sit over there. I'll sit over there, it looks cleaner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，你别添乱了。我不同意。去，那边坐着去。我要坐那里，看着更干净。

yingyinNormal.en: Your joke? Well, I think 'the Hef' would disagree, which is why he sent me a check for one hundred ah-dollars.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的笑话？海夫纳（花花公子创办人）可不同意，所以他寄了这张支票给我，一百美元。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, number one: in matters of physics, I have the final say. In matters of neuroscience, you have the final say. Unless I disagree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 规则一：跟物理有关的，我有最终决定权。跟神经科学有关的，你有最终决定权。除非我不同意。

yingyinNormal.en: And if you disagree, I'd recommend you have a cat scan to look for a tumor pressing on the cognitive processing centers of your brain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你不同意，我建议你去做一个X光断层扫描，看看是不是有肿瘤压迫到了你大脑的认知处理单元。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I totally disagree. No, I think it's fine for a guy to do something like that. Especially an actor. I mean, not that you need to. Your eyebrows are..
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我完全不同意，我觉得男生那样做没有什么，尤其是演员。我不是说你有那个必要，你的眉毛…

yingyinNormal.en: You know what? I'm with Leonard, this isn't cool. Thank you. I disagree. Penny is a strong, independent woman. The more you try to control her, the more she'll push back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我支持莱纳德？这样是不对的。谢谢。我不同意。佩妮是一个独立而坚强的新女性。你越想掌控她，她反抗越强烈。

yingyinNormal.en: I would disagree. It's all sentimental. It does work, if you belong together with someone, then it works. Trouble is finding someone you belong with. Belongs with you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不同意，这种东西太伤感了。可以的，如果你注定跟某人在一起，就会幸福。麻烦的是去找到命中注定那个人，属于你的人。

yingyinNormal.en: I beg to disagree. A girlfriend shall be deemed quote living with un-quote Leonard when she has stayed over for A: ten consecutive nights.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有不同意见，某女性被认定为跟莱纳德，前引号同居，后引号的时间条件是，第一：连续十晚。

yingyinNormal.en: And even though this is a college where Facebook was born, my hope is that you would try to go out and have more face-to-face conversations with people you may disagree with.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尽管Facebook在这里诞生，我希望各位要去尝试和那些与你持不同意见的人进行更多的面对面交流。

yingyinNormal.en: Yo, bozo. Yes? A true friend always lets her friend know what she is really thinking. That is the definition of friendship. Is there anybody here who could possibly disagree with that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 喂，这位大哥。什么事？一个真正的朋友总会让朋友知道自己的想法，那才是友情的定义。在座的有谁持不同意见吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Why didn't you disagree with him, Riley?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你当时为什么不反驳他，莱丽？

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry, is he waiting for someone to disagree?
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，他是在等着有人提出反对意见吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Hate to disagree with you, sir, but those aren't onions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 抱歉，长官，这些不是洋葱。

yingyinNormal.en: I believe the internal revenue service would strongly disagree.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我相信国税局会强烈反对。

yingyinNormal.en: Those who disagree with my actions, speak now without repercussion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 若是有人不赞同朕的做法现在说出来，朕恕他无罪。

yingyinNormal.en: Maya, how can I disagree with what he said, if what he said was true?
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛雅，你叫我怎么反驳他啊，他说的明明是对的啊？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

derivative_info_list.mean: adj. 讨厌的；令人不快的；脾气坏的；不友善的
n. 意见不一；不同意；不一致；不符

word_family.mean: v. 有意见分歧；有不同观点；不一致；不相当；不同意；有害；不适宜

sense_info_list.en: (of statements or accounts) be inconsistent or fail to correspond

examination_example.sentence: They <highlight>disagree</highlight> about the future of AI technology.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们对人工智能技术的未来意见不一。

examination_example.sentence: People <highlight>disagree</highlight> as to who should do what.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于谁应该做什么，人们意见不一。

examination_example.sentence: Development agencies <highlight>disagree</highlight> regarding how to tackle environment issues while ensuring economic progress.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于如何在确保经济进步的同时解决环境问题，发展机构意见不一。

sense_info_list.en: have or express a different opinion

examination_example.sentence: At other times, they may <highlight>disagree</highlight> with the spirit of the procedure—the effort demanded, the time consumed, the lack of potential effectiveness.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在其他时候，他们可能不同意程序的精神——所需的努力、所消耗的时间、缺乏潜在的有效性。

examination_example.sentence: Employees have the power to speak up, give feedback, <highlight>disagree</highlight> and discuss problems in real time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 员工有权畅所欲言，给予反馈，提出异议，并实时讨论问题。

examination_example.sentence: He <highlight>disagreed</highlight> with the governor on higher education policies.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他不同意州长关于高等教育政策的观点。

examination_example.sentence: Professor Wilding <highlight>disagrees</highlight> that labelling a high proportion of the population as having a disease removes personal responsibility or may overwhelm health services.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 威尔丁教授不同意将高比例的人口标记为患有疾病会免除个人责任或可能使卫生服务不堪重负。

examination_example.sentence: Arrhenius calculated the capability of carbon dioxide to trap heat in the Earth's atmosphere, but other chemists <highlight>disagreed</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Arrhenius计算了二氧化碳在地球大气中捕获热量的能力，但其他化学家并不认同。

examination_example.sentence: Survey respondents <highlight>disagree</highlight> over whether this generation will follow in their parents' footsteps.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 调查对象对这一代人是否会追随父母的脚步持不同意见。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
